		<div id="comment_body_45447907"><p><nobr> <wbr></nobr></p><div class="quote"><p>...to weed out the burner phones from the high-quality ones.</p></div><p>What do you want to bet those "high quality" numbers quickly become a target for telemarketers to plunder?<nobr> <wbr></nobr>:p</p></div>
	</div>

