<div id="comment_45448047" class="cw">
	<div id="comment_top_45448047" class="commentTop newcomment">
		<div class="title">
			<h4><a id="comment_link_45448047" name="comment_link_45448047" href="//slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=4453811&amp;cid=45448047" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(45448047)" >'Things' haven't changed all that much </a>


