	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_45449819"><p>As someone who works at a business who could not operate without this type of information I understand it's necessity.   It's sad but it's necessary in today's world.   Just like IP reputation, device, address reputation and many other things, a vendor, a provider, or person on the other end of the world can only know so much given a certain piece of information.   It's incredibly valuable to know if someone is calling from a VOIP number when you're running a high risk business.   Some times for some transa<span class="substr"> </span></p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_45449819">

